    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrows and Antiquity是一款弓箭竞速FPS游戏, 你可以在其中掌握独特的箭矢, 发现隐藏的捷径, 从而以惊人的速度征服试炼. 阿耳忒弥斯拥有一把传说之弓, 只属于真正的箭术大师. 你能完成她的试炼吗?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>追求完美</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握一大批独特的箭矢, 每种箭矢都拥有强大的能力. 发现捷径, 发明巧妙技巧, 优化路线, 从而赢得奖牌, 在排行榜上攀升! 射偏了吗? 立即重启, 追求完美通关.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310430/extras/9c7a104a7c0016710c04562b69ddeb2e.poster.avif?t=1758245239\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310430/extras/9c7a104a7c0016710c04562b69ddeb2e.webm?t=1758245239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310430/extras/9c7a104a7c0016710c04562b69ddeb2e.mp4?t=1758245239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在线幻影</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他弓箭手的幻影重播竞速. 学习他们的路线, 射箭方式与技巧. 然后击败他们.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310430/extras/dc84b30bcbaef2065782bbcf54d6339b.poster.avif?t=1758245239\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310430/extras/dc84b30bcbaef2065782bbcf54d6339b.webm?t=1758245239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310430/extras/dc84b30bcbaef2065782bbcf54d6339b.mp4?t=1758245239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收藏品</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找隐藏的礼物和卷轴, 从而解锁改变游戏的遗物. 赢得奖牌, 从阿耳忒弥斯的私人武器库中获得稀有弓!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310430/extras/061cc0afd676cda426d238797f14fdb0.poster.avif?t=1758245239\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310430/extras/061cc0afd676cda426d238797f14fdb0.webm?t=1758245239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310430/extras/061cc0afd676cda426d238797f14fdb0.mp4?t=1758245239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精通箭术</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战多样地形与独特考验. 无人将其全部掌握. 你会是第一个吗?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310430/extras/31045939c08ea7b11501a65b7ccca815.poster.avif?t=1758245239\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310430/extras/31045939c08ea7b11501a65b7ccca815.webm?t=1758245239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310430/extras/31045939c08ea7b11501a65b7ccca815.mp4?t=1758245239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2>",
